verses.verse: The LORD reigneth; he is apparelled with majesty; the LORD is apparelled, he hath girded himself with strength: The world also is stablished, That it cannot be moved
Thy throne is established of old: Thou art from everlasting
The floods have lifted up, O LORD, the floods have lifted up their voice; the floods lift up their waves
Above the voices of many waters, the mighty breakers of the sea, the LORD on high is mighty
Thy testimonies are very sure: Holiness becometh thine house, O LORD, for evermore.
